  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You are specially modified droid used to house a shard. Shards are sentient crystals native to the planet Orax, roughly a foot in length, that communicate with each other through pulses of light. While inhabiting a specialized droid host, shards are able to overcome the droid's inability to wield the Force, granting the following benefits:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Increase an ability score of your choice by 1, to a maximum of 20.</li>\n<li>You lose the Force-Insensitive special trait.</li>\n<li>You can cast the <em>sense force</em> force power once per day. Wisdom or Charisma (your choice) is your forcecasting ability for this power.</li></ul>",
